reviewText:
Mosaic maze is a precision platformer by Raw Lion Workshop

The first-impressions-video can be found here: https://youtu.be/rcE0fYFM-Ao

Here are some points about the game:
It gets really difficult really fast
No soundtrack, just soundbits
Bonus unlocks and variety mechanics keep the game engaging
Death can be unecessarilly punishing at times
Reset button to get out of softlock would be nice to have
All in all I am pleased with this game and would recommend it especially to those people who like to conquer a challenging platformer.

reviewText: Its a good game. The respawn locations are very inconsistent and very frustrating putting you very behind corners which you've already passed by. Untill that is changed I probably won't go back to the game
